@HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7139

# Health check
GET {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/health

### Get Service Status
GET {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/

### Check Availability
POST {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/inventory/availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotelId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "roomTypeId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001",
  "checkIn": "2024-12-01T15:00:00Z",
  "checkOut": "2024-12-05T11:00:00Z",
  "roomCount": 2
}

### Create Room Hold
POST {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/inventory/holds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002",
  "hotelId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "roomTypeId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001",
  "checkIn": "2024-12-01T15:00:00Z",
  "checkOut": "2024-12-05T11:00:00Z",
  "roomCount": 1,
  "holdDuration": "00:15:00"
}

### Get Room Hold - Replace {holdId} with actual hold ID from create response
@holdId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003
GET {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/inventory/holds/{{holdId}}

### Release Room Hold - Replace {holdId} with actual hold ID
POST {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/inventory/holds/{{holdId}}/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002",
  "reason": "Customer cancelled"
}

### Confirm Room Booking - Replace {holdId} with actual hold ID
POST {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/inventory/holds/{{holdId}}/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002",
  "paymentId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174004"
}

### Health Check UI (if available)
GET {{HotelBookingSystem.InventoryService.Api_HostAddress}}/healthchecks-ui 